Package: sparsefactor
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference Techniques for Sparse Factor Models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2020-01-19
Author: Yong See Foo [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yong See Foo <fooy1@student.unimelb.edu.au>
Description: This package provides two approaches to inference for sparse factor models: Gibbs sampling and variational inference. Additionally, a relabelling algorithm is implemented to address issues which arise from label switching and sign switching.
License: BSD-2
Imports: 
